Maybe that's some sort of
slang that I don't know.

00:07:49.390 --> 00:07:51.650
RETO MEIER: Yeah don't
ask, don't tell.

00:07:51.650 --> 00:07:54.820
IAN NI-LEWIS: I think that the
main objection that we had to

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:56.610
the UI was the camera button.

00:07:56.610 --> 00:07:58.280
What do you think, Ramzi?

00:07:58.280 --> 00:07:59.840
RAMZI RIZK: I absolutely
agree.

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:03.000
I mean, you guys definitely
know this.

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:06.360
It's a bit of a challenge trying
to keep up with design

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:07.410
guidelines in a lot of ways.

00:08:07.410 --> 00:08:10.310
And especially, like you said,
when it comes to photography

00:08:10.310 --> 00:08:13.230
apps, you have your
own spirit.

00:08:13.230 --> 00:08:14.830
And we're a very design-driven
company.

00:08:14.830 --> 00:08:17.430
So we have a team of people
