So they started basically
looking and realized that

00:08:23.200 --> 00:08:26.140
issue when you mentioned
it last Friday, was it?

00:08:26.140 --> 00:08:28.480
And they are looking at
ways to improve that.

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:29.790
So it definitely
